translation[5]{c,v,t}:
  28,1,Tâ-Sîn-Mîm
  28,2,Ezi ziiVesi zeNcwadi ecacileyo
  28,3,Sizicengceleza kuwe zivela kwiindaba zikaMûsâ noFir’awn ngenyaniso kubantu abakholwayo
  28,4,"Inene, uFir’awn waziphakamisa ezweni wenza nabantu balo baba ziimvaba ngeemvaba, ecinezela iqela elithile kubo, egwinta oonyana babo agcine abasetyhini babo. Inene, yena wayengomnye wabenzi bobubi"
  28,5,"Ke kaloku Thina Saye Sathanda ukuba Sibonise uBabalo kwabo babecinezelekile elizweni, Sabenza baziinkokeli, Sabenza baba ziindlalifa"